Text: Kudos to you, sir. I started looking over the many items up u/l and I was blown away at the volume and diversity of materials.  I can only guess that somewhere out there is a library server and scanner both working overtime.  Thank you for your diligence.  Would it be possible to get the American Journal of Nursing, vol 99, #12?  If not, no worries.  Meanwhile, I'll continue to seed the 15 items downloaded already.
